# Half-Life and Parameter Determination

10. The concentration of drug X is 10 mg/L 3 hours postdose and 6 mg/L 8 hours postdose. What is the half-life of the drug?



::: {#22 .cell execution_count=1}
``` {.julia .cell-code}
Cₜ₁ = 10
t1 = 3

Cₜ₂ = 6
t2 = 8
Cu = "mg/L"

th, th_lat = th_latex(Cₜ₁,t1,Cₜ₂,t2,Cu)

display(th_lat)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display .cell-output-markdown}
$t_{1} = 3\ hr, \ $$t_{2} = 8\ hr, \ $\begin{equation*}
t_h = \frac{0.693 \cdot \left( 8 - 3 \right)}{\log\left( 10 \right) - \log\left( 6 \right)} = 6.783\ mg/L
\end{equation*}

:::
:::





-----

